Subject: DWR Stranded Cost Update
Mime-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=us-ascii
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 7bit
X-From: Alan Comnes <Alan Comnes/ENRON@enronXgate>
X-To: Jeff Dasovich <Jeff Dasovich/NA/Enron@Enron>, Jennifer Thome <Jennifer Thome/ENRON@enronXgate>, Richard Shapiro <Richard Shapiro/NA/Enron@Enron>, James D Steffes <James D Steffes/NA/Enron@Enron>, Susan J Mara <Susan J Mara/NA/Enron@ENRON>, Dave Perrino <Dave Perrino/SF/ECT@ECT>, Ban Sharma <Ban Sharma/ENRON_DEVELOPMENT@ENRON_DEVELOPMENT>, Tim Belden <Tim Belden/ENRON@enronXgate>, Ray Alvarez <Ray Alvarez/NA/Enron@ENRON>
